{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3015_00_01","textHome":"我，最喜欢大自然了。@花鸟鱼虫都喜欢，还有玩耍，我也最喜欢了！@不管是在外面，还是在家里！@学习？学习也……喜欢哦！@真的真的！我说真的啦！@不过要是可以的话……我想一直玩耍下去！@诶，不行吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3015_00_18","textHome":"我喜欢喝茶，所以想有一天能挑战一下茶道！@虽然周围的人会说我不太适合，@但才没有这种事呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":301550}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3015_00_19","textHome":"哈！……等一下……难道说我……变强了！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3015_00_20","textHome":"我也感觉到了！@刚刚……发生了什么好事对吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":301550,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3015_00_21","textHome":"家附近有一片树林，我一直在那里尽情玩耍。@不管是和丽良还有其他朋友一起玩，@还是自己一个人玩，都非常有趣！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3015_00_22","textHome":"自己一个人的时候，我会在树林里建造别墅。@用大树旁捡到的树枝和家里的瓦楞纸之类的，@来制作墙壁和天花板，然后再拿本书钻进去！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":301550,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3015_00_23","textHome":"过去，我在树林里建造过一座自己的别墅！@然后我把它进一步扩建，@最终建成了「未都庄园」！@用来玩的道具都是自己制作的！@还和丽良她们一起玩过哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":301550,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":301550,"motion":1}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3015_50_24"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":301550,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.e